data.text: @SoccerNana Do you have a LINK to a report that explains all of what you're talking about? We have 280 characters, yes, but it's good journalism to link to more expository information. (Yes, I'm being a writing cop. Writing cops built me.)
@QueenPhillippa 😂the statement should be “recorded a ‘message’!” Twitter needs an edit function!

@QueenPhillippa This is a deterrent; trying to make the Windsor exhibition of the May 2018 Royal Wedding outfits fail.  The D&DoS recorded a recording that is also a part of the display. They’re trying to make folks doubt what’s being said in the recording.
